divs: Sighting DetailsI reported a sighting yeasterday and this morning I was out on padio again and think I figured out what I saw friday, It must have been a meteor comming straight at me and burning out as it came in, giving the illusion that it was pulling away till gone from site, sorry for bothering you with this. thanks Dave.
